high_descs: Turn right and take a small step to your right then walk forward to the counter.
Pick up the fork that's in front of you to the right of the stove.
Turn around and take a step then turn left to face the sink.
Wash the fork in the left sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn left to face the counter again.
Open the drawer under the counter to the right of the stove and put the clean fork in there then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork in the drawer.
